{"tid":1763535,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"科技大學校長史維: 年輕人不會放棄香港，香港現在的問題並非大灣區能夠處理到","createTime":"2019-11-30T12:12:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T12:52:36.000Z","uid":51271,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5e5977bb6799f977617fe363c7945e33dedae687","tid":1763535,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T12:12:29.000Z","msg":"科技大學校長史維說，社會傾向為不同人貼上標籤，要令不同立場的人能夠溝通十分困難，但仍然非常重要。他認為，溝通未必可以解決所有問題，但可以幫大家找出一個方向。<br />\n<br />\n史維出席一個研討會時說，社會上的既得利益者希望珍惜現狀，年輕人則較悲觀，擔心前途，亦認為自己的聲音沒法被聽見，因此走向社會運動。<br />\n<br />\n但他相信兩者未必是衝突的，例如部分年輕人即使對政府不滿，但仍然希望讀書學習，希望有未來。<br />\n<br />\n被問到大灣區的發展會否是年輕人的出路，史維說，年輕人不會放棄香港，香港現在的問題並非大灣區能夠處理到。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1495319-20191130.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1495319-20191130.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=ZahK9au6JYDyKCuDEpipf%2BCrFKAYikA6kkEaryQCE%2B8%3D&h=b814f3c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1495319-20191130.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=1b935cc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1495319-20191130.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n哇，佢都算幾有膽量去屌"},{"pid":"433591cd03dc15a3da09a921e93e7f0e280a1fa2","tid":1763535,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T12:13:29.000Z","msg":"人之將死？"},{"pid":"29fae4f2b2b14af31e21487a7ceb96b18053024a","tid":1763535,"uid":254766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T12:13:42.000Z","msg":"好 不過唔好打飛機 推行動post"},{"pid":"38f3b806843ca19c82786dcab60b545e2ec9a744","tid":1763535,"uid":332804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T12:16:11.000Z","msg":"我地要講嘅已經講曬，而家係港共中港冇誠意傾咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d734ba0e93a19624b081646d9ae65d861d8f612a","tid":1763535,"uid":3149